- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new method for anomaly detection using a machine learning model, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): Anomaly detection is often used in security applications, and the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed method in real-world environments.
